OL,3,CMan with autism and ADHD fears losing
OL,4,CPIP payment
OL,6,FITV News Meridian's Tom Savvides
OL,7,Fspeaks to Owen Young about Government
OL,8,Fchanges to welfare support
OL,10,FA man from Kent with autism and ADHD
OL,11,Fsays he will struggle to make ends
OL,12,Fmeet if he loses funding in the
OL,13,Fgovernment's shake-up of disability
OL,14,Fpayments.
OL,16,FOwen Young, from Margate, fears he
OL,17,Fwill lose his Personal Independence
OL,18,FPayment, known as PIP, when payments
OL,19,Fare reassessed under the Government's
OL,20,Fwelfare reforms next year.
