OL,3,CMan with autism and ADHD fears losing
OL,4,CPIP payment
OL,6,FThe 25-year old uses a community shop
OL,7,Fin Margate to pick up cheap food and
OL,8,Fother essentials. He's been diagnosed
OL,9,Fwith Autism and struggles with
OL,10,Feveryday life.
OL,12,FOwen said, "They're taking money away
OL,13,Ffrom people who are already struggling
OL,14,Fand scraping by to survive.
OL,16,F"We're not living in luxury. We're
OL,17,Fjust wanting to be treated like human
OL,18,Fbeings, to give us that opportunity to
OL,19,Fthrive in a community and in a world
OL,20,Fwhich isn't exactly the easiest for us.
