OL,6,F"To simply go ahead and take the money
OL,7,Faway and go, 'now look for work', I
OL,8,Fdon't get the practicality or the
OL,9,Flogic."
OL,11,FThe Government has announced welfare
OL,12,Fwill be cut, with changes to Personal
OL,13,FIndependence Payment and universal
OL,14,Fcredit.
OL,16,FIt says that the number of people
OL,17,Freceiving PIP has risen rapidly and is
OL,18,Fbecoming "unsustainable".
