OL,4,CPIP payment
OL,6,FChancellor Rachel Reeves MP said the
OL,7,FGovernment is committed to getting
OL,8,Fyoung people into work
OL,10,FTreasury Minister James Murray MP
OL,11,Fsaid, "The welfare system, as it is
OL,12,Fright now, cannot carry on and it's
OL,13,Fbroken.
OL,15,F"It's not helping people to get back
OL,16,Finto work where they can. And it's not
OL,17,Fsustainable to make sure the support
OL,18,Fis there for those in greatest need.
OL,19,FThat's why the reforms that we set
OL,20,Fout, it's so important."
